combopacks.name: dried vegetables
combopacks.description: Made from delicious vegetables, tubers, green fruits such as: bananas, sweet potatoes, taro, jackfruit, carrots, bitter melon ..... The dried mixed dish is a delicious and attractive gift for all visitors when set foot in Da Lat - The city of flowers, jams and vegetables. From modern advanced drying equipment, it keeps the natural flavor of the fruit, the aroma, deliciousness, crunchiness and very good taste. Provides many essential nutrients and minerals for the body.
